
# Netlify redirects - Force canonical domain and HTTPS
http://wavementor.com/*       https://www.wavementor.com/:splat  301!
https://wavementor.com/*      https://www.wavementor.com/:splat  301!
http://www.wavementor.com/*   https://www.wavementor.com/:splat  301!

# Handle specific problematic redirects from Search Console
